        <description>
            The VESPA portal connects data services responsive to the
            EPN-TAP protocol. EPN-TAP services describe all products individually,
            and cover many fields of Solar System(s) studies. The portal also
            queries PDAP services at dataset level. Associated web services and
            command-line mode are available. VESPA has been developed in the frame
            of the EU founded Europlanet programme, to adapt the astronomy Virtual
            Observatory (VO) to Planetary Science. Data selection can be passed to
            VO display and analysis tools via the SAMP protocol. 
       </description>
